SELECT DISTINCT a.FIELD_NAME, CASE WHEN e.[CONTENT] IS NULL THEN CAST(e.[XMLCONTENT] AS nvarchar(MAX)) ELSE e.[CONTENT] END AS Content, head.FIELD_NAME AS Header_Field_Name, head.CONTENT AS Header_Content, d.DOCUMENT_NUMBER, c.FEED_COMPANY_ID FROM dbo.DOCUMENT_FIELD_VALUE AS e INNER JOIN dbo.DOCUMENT_FIELD_ATTRIBUTE AS a ON a.DOCUMENT_FIELD_ID = e.DOCUMENT_FIELD_ID INNER JOIN dbo.[DOCUMENT] AS d ON d.DOCUMENT_ID = e.DOCUMENT_ID INNER JOIN dbo.LINE_OF_BUSINESS AS l ON l.BUSINESS_ID = d.BUSINESS_ID INNER JOIN dbo.COMPANY AS c ON c.COMPANY_ID = l.COMPANY_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT eh.DOCUMENT_ID, eh.LANGUAGE_ID, ah.FIELD_NAME, eh.CONTENT FROM DOCUMENT_FIELD_VALUE AS eh INNER JOIN DOCUMENT_FIELD_ATTRIBUTE ah ON eh.DOCUMENT_FIELD_ID = ah.DOCUMENT_FIELD_ID WHERE eh.DATA_TYPE = 'TEXT' ) AS head ON head.DOCUMENT_ID = e.DOCUMENT_ID AND head.LANGUAGE_ID = e.LANGUAGE_ID AND head.FIELD_NAME = CONCAT(a.FIELD_NAME, 'h')
WHERE c.FEED_COMPANY_ID IN (1003, 1005) AND (((a.FIELD_NAME like 'M12%' OR a.FIELD_NAME like 'M11%') AND d.DOCUMENT_NUMBER = '966636') OR (a.FIELD_NAME like 'M15%' AND d.DOCUMENT_NUMBER = '426747'))
AND e.DATA_TYPE IN ('TABLE', 'CHART') AND e.LANGUAGE_ID = 1
AND a.IS_ACTIVE = 1 AND d.IS_ACTIVE = 1 AND l.IS_ACTIVE = 1 FOR xml AUTO, ROOT ('ArrayOfpub_Historic_Field_Data'), ELEMENTS
